showAllCreatedBusiness: Here are all the businesses you've created on our platform
deleteBusinessHelpText:
If you delete these businesses from your account:

  • Some business information (name, address, etc.) will still appear on search engines like Google, Bing, etc.
  • All content on the VietSearch Business Page (website, posts, photos, videos, etc.) that you’ve published for these businesses will be deleted.
  • Linked VietSearch Ads campaigns will cease to function.
  • Anyone else managing the deleted businesses will lose access to them.
  • Data for deleted businesses cannot be recovered.

If the business is closed, you should mark it as permanently closed before deleting it.

If you don’t want to delete a business, you can transfer ownership instead.
